message:
LOOKING FOR SUMMER SUBLET @ The Marshall
 
I'm looking for female sublet for the summer at The Marshall in Dinkytown, mid-May through August (I'll pay rent for the month of May). The apartment is a 2 bed/2 bath. You would be sharing a room and a bathroom with one other person. Rent also includes an underground garage parking spot. Utilities are around 15-20 dollars a month.

Rent is $535 and the parking spot is $135. I am willing to negotiate. Message me if you're interested or if you know anyone that would be interested!!
